---
source: src/tests.rs
expression: render_command_help(&refs)
---
Set files on an input[type=file] element

Usage: bl upload [OPTIONS] <selector> <files>...

Arguments:
  <selector>  CSS selector (or map ref) for the input[type=file] element
  <files>...  One or more file paths to set on the input

Options:
      --headless  Hide browser window (visible by default)
  -v, --verbose   Enable debug logging
      --json      Output as JSON
  -h, --help      Print help

Examples:
  bl upload "input[type=file]" ./photo.jpg
  # Upload a single file

  bl upload "#file-input" ./photo.jpg ./doc.pdf
  # Upload multiple files
